cat << EOF
Clutter-GTK is a library providing facilities to integrate Clutter into GTK+
applications and vice versa.
Clutter-GTK provides a GTK+ widget, GtkClutterEmbed, for embedding the a Clutter
stage into any GtkContainer; and GtkClutterActor, a Clutter actor for embedding
any GtkWidget inside a Clutter stage.
EOF
